Maintainer: Gentry White <gentry.white@qut.edu.au>
Description: Draw samples from the direct sampling spatial prior model
        as described in G. White, D. Sun, P. Speckman (2019)
        <arXiv:1906.05575>. The basic model assumes a Gaussian
        likelihood and derives a spatial prior based on thin-plate
        splines.
